      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "requiredLevel": 1,
      "achievedLevel": 1,
      "factorStatus": "not-assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Not required at MRL 2; single experimental replicate per operating point with documented blood preparation is sufficient.",
      "rationale": "Each of the five operating points tested in triplicate using independently prepared blood samples from the same porcine source. Coefficient of variation for NIH across replicates was below 8% at all points. Formal statistical sample size justification not required at MRL 2."
    },
